title: Massive Queue times as a level 11 in blind pick mode.
body:
I've just had two very long queue timers, my last queue was 16 minutes, and this queue is already up to 7. Last time, I was playing at Midday, and this time I'm playing at 3pm. Why is it taking so long?

My win rate is 16-1 which probably raises my mmr, but it shouldn't matter that much, should it?

replies.body: Recently, people have been experiencing connection issues. Could just be extremely low server populace atm.
